00:38:00,072 --> 00:38:03,033
JUST CAN'T
BE DONE THAT WAY.

555
00:38:03,075 --> 00:38:05,035
YEAH. I GUESS
YOU'RE RIGHT.

556
00:38:05,077 --> 00:38:06,537
IT CAN'T BE.

557
00:38:06,578 --> 00:38:08,539
WE'LL JUST, UH...

558
00:38:08,580 --> 00:38:10,541
STICK TO
THE ORIGINAL PLAN,

559
00:38:10,582 --> 00:38:12,042
AND, UM...

