568
00:39:54,186 --> 00:39:56,647
I GUESS
WITH YOU SO, UH...

569
00:39:56,688 --> 00:40:02,653
CLEAN AND PRETTY
AND EVERYTHING, I, UH...

570
00:40:02,694 --> 00:40:04,655
YEAH.

