577
00:40:29,721 --> 00:40:33,183
[TELEPHONE RINGS]

578
00:40:33,225 --> 00:41:57,267
[RING]

579
00:41:57,309 --> 00:42:48,485
OK.

580
00:42:48,527 --> 00:42:52,489
[TELEPHONE RINGS]

581
00:42:52,531 --> 00:42:54,992
[RING]

582
00:42:55,033 --> 00:42:56,493
HELLO?

583
00:42:56,535 --> 00:42:57,494
COLLIE.

584
00:42:57,536 --> 00:42:59,997
COLLIE?

585
00:43:00,038 --> 00:43:01,999
LOOK, FELLA,
WHERE ARE YOU?

586
00:43:02,040 --> 00:43:04,501
RIGHT WHERE
I'VE ALWAYS BEEN.

587
00:43:04,543 --> 00:43:06,003
I SEE.

588
00:43:06,044 --> 00:43:09,006
YOU REMEMBER,
I ONLY AGREED NOT TO SEE HER.

589
00:43:09,047 --> 00:43:12,009
I DIDN'T SAY
I WOULDN'T TELEPHONE.

590
00:43:12,050 --> 00:43:15,012
YOU'RE A MAN
OF YOUR WORD, DOC.

591
00:43:15,053 --> 00:43:16,513
I DIDN'T
SAY ANYTHING

592
00:43:16,555 --> 00:43:18,515
THAT SHOULD
HAVE ALARMED HER.

593
00:43:18,557 --> 00:43:22,019
ON THE CONTRARY,
I WAS CAREFUL TO REASSURE HER.

594
00:43:22,060 --> 00:43:24,521
THAT MAKES HER
KIND OF CRAZY, DOESN'T IT?

595
00:43:24,563 --> 00:43:26,523
SHE SHOULDN'T
HAVE BEEN ALARMED,

596
00:43:26,565 --> 00:43:28,525
AND SHE SHOULD
HAVE BEEN REASSURED.

597
00:43:28,567 --> 00:43:31,528
BUT IT TURNED OUT
THE EXACT OTHER WAY.

598
00:43:31,570 --> 00:43:34,031
SHE DIDN'T
REACT PROPERLY.

599
00:43:34,072 --> 00:43:37,034
SHE'S ABNORMAL,
ISN'T SHE, DOC?

600
00:43:37,075 --> 00:43:41,038
I'M TERRIBLY SORRY
IT'S TURNED OUT THIS WAY, COLLIE,

601
00:43:41,079 --> 00:43:44,041
BUT YOU HAVE TO UNDERSTAND
MY ONLY INTEREST

602
00:43:44,082 --> 00:43:46,543
IS IN DOING
WHAT'S BEST FOR YOU.

603
00:43:46,585 --> 00:43:48,545
REMEMBER, COLLIE,
WE'RE FRIENDS.

604
00:43:48,587 --> 00:43:51,048
HA! YEAH.

605
00:43:51,089 --> 00:43:54,051
YEAH.
I REMEMBER THAT, DOC.

606
00:43:54,092 --> 00:43:55,052
YOU'LL
STAY THERE THEN?

607
00:43:55,093 --> 00:43:57,554
GIVE ME A CHANCE
TO STRAIGHTEN THIS OUT?

608
00:43:57,596 --> 00:43:58,555
NO. I'M LEAVING NOW.

609
00:43:58,597 --> 00:44:00,057
NO! NO, COLLIE.

610
00:44:00,098 --> 00:44:03,560
IF YOU DON'T
FEEL THAT YOU CAN STAY THERE,

611
00:44:03,602 --> 00:44:05,562
YOU MUST COME BACK
OVER HERE.

612
00:44:05,604 --> 00:44:08,065
WE'LL GO AHEAD
JUST AS WE PLANNED.

613
00:44:08,106 --> 00:44:10,567
I'M HITTING
THE TRAIL NOW, DOC.

614
00:44:10,609 --> 00:44:12,569
DON'T TRY TO
PICK UP THAT TRAIL,

615
00:44:12,611 --> 00:44:22,579
BECAUSE IF YOU DO...

616
00:44:22,621 --> 00:44:25,082
HI, KID.

617
00:44:25,123 --> 00:44:29,586
[TELEPHONE RINGS]

618
00:44:29,628 --> 00:44:35,092
[RING]

619
00:44:35,133 --> 00:44:41,598
[RING]

620
00:44:41,640 --> 00:44:45,602
HI, UNCLE BUD.

621
00:44:45,644 --> 00:44:48,605
YOU KNOW,
FAY CALLED ME.

622
00:44:48,647 --> 00:44:50,107
WAS PRETTY UPSET.

623
00:44:50,149 --> 00:44:53,610
I'M NOT SURE I REALLY
GOT IT ALL RIGHT.

624
00:44:53,652 --> 00:44:56,613
I KNOW
WHAT HAPPENED.

625
00:44:56,655 --> 00:44:58,115
HELL OF A NOTE.

626
00:44:58,157 --> 00:45:01,118
TWO OF YOU WERE
HITTING IT OFF SO WELL,

627
00:45:01,160 --> 00:45:03,620
AND THEN SOMETHING LIKE
THAT HAS TO HAPPEN.

628
00:45:03,662 --> 00:45:06,123
BUT SHE'LL
GET OUT OF IT.

629
00:45:06,165 --> 00:45:08,625
SOON AS SHE GETS
USED TO THE NOTION,

630
00:45:08,667 --> 00:45:10,127
SHE'LL SNAP
OUT OF IT.

631
00:45:10,169 --> 00:45:11,628
JUST LIKE YOU,
UNCLE BUD?

632
00:45:11,670 --> 00:45:13,130
YEAH. JUST LIKE ME.

633
00:45:13,172 --> 00:45:16,133
NOTHING BOTHERS ME.

634
00:45:16,175 --> 00:45:20,637
YOU KNOW, A MAN'S A MAN.
ALL THAT.

635
00:45:20,679 --> 00:45:28,145
BET YOU'D LIKE A DRINK.

636
00:45:28,187 --> 00:45:31,148
HE LET ME KNOW THAT AFTER
THINKING IT OVER,

637
00:45:31,190 --> 00:45:33,650
HE DECIDED WE SHOULD
GO AHEAD WITH EVERYTHING

638
00:45:33,692 --> 00:45:35,152
JUST AS PLANNED.

639
00:45:35,194 --> 00:45:38,655
FAY WOULDN'T BE IN THE CAR
TO HELP WITH THE KID,

640
00:45:38,697 --> 00:45:41,158
BUT HE WAS CONVINCED
I COULD HANDLE IT.

641
00:45:41,200 --> 00:45:43,660
I SAW HOW,
FROM HIS POINT OF VIEW,

642
00:45:43,702 --> 00:45:45,162
THE SITUATION
HAD ACTUALLY IMPROVED.

643
00:45:45,204 --> 00:45:47,164
I'D NEVER MEANT
ANYTHING TO HIM,

644
00:45:47,206 --> 00:45:50,167
AND NOW THAT I DIDN'T
MEAN ANYTHING TO FAY,

645
00:45:50,209 --> 00:45:53,170
AND SINCE HE REALIZED
HE COULD FAKE THE JOB

646
00:45:53,212 --> 00:45:54,671
AND STILL CASH IN...

647
00:45:54,713 --> 00:45:58,175
YOU'D HAVE TO BE BLIND NOT
TO SEE WHAT WAS COMING.

648
00:45:58,217 --> 00:46:00,677
I WAS DUE TO GET KILLED,

649
00:46:00,719 --> 00:46:04,181
AND UNCLE BUD WAS DUE--
OR THOUGHT HE WAS--

650
00:46:04,223 --> 00:46:22,199
TO BE A HERO.

651
00:46:22,241 --> 00:46:27,204
HEY!

