677
00:50:53,637 --> 00:50:56,598
SOMETHING THAT WOULD
PULL THEM INTO THE DEAL

678
00:50:56,640 --> 00:51:18,620
AND HOLD THEM IN IT.

679
00:51:18,662 --> 00:51:21,123
ROGERS,
HELP SAVE MY ASS.

680
00:51:21,165 --> 00:51:30,632
MAYBE A QUICK
AROUND-THE-BLOCK?

681
00:51:30,674 --> 00:51:32,134
APPRECIATE IT,
BUDDY.

682
00:51:32,176 --> 00:51:35,637
BESIDES, I WANTED TO TALK
TO YOU ABOUT CHARLIE.

683
00:51:35,679 --> 00:51:38,140
WHAT'S HAPPENED
TO HIM ANYWAY, ROG?

684
00:51:38,182 --> 00:51:39,141
WHAT KIND
OF SHOVING AROUND

685
00:51:39,183 --> 00:51:41,143
ARE HIS PARENTS
GIVING HIM?

686
00:51:41,185 --> 00:51:42,144
SHOVING AROUND?

687
00:51:42,186 --> 00:51:44,646
I GUESS I DON'T
KNOW WHAT YOU MEAN.

688
00:51:44,688 --> 00:51:47,149
NEVER MIND. I KNOW
HOW THEY TREAT HIM.

689
00:51:47,191 --> 00:51:51,153
HE'S BEEN SICK FOR YEARS,
AND HE'S GETTING SICKER.

690
00:51:51,195 --> 00:51:52,154
THE WORSE HE GETS,

691
00:51:52,196 --> 00:51:54,656
THE TOUGHER
THEY MAKE IT FOR HIM.

692
00:51:54,698 --> 00:51:56,158
IF I WAS BIGGER,

693
00:51:56,200 --> 00:52:00,662
I'D GET A CLUB AND...

694
00:52:00,704 --> 00:52:02,164
SOMETHING WRONG,
ROGERS?

695
00:52:02,206 --> 00:52:04,166
WANT ME TO DUCK DOWN?

696
00:52:04,208 --> 00:52:06,668
THESE ARE JUST
SOME FRIENDS OF MINE.

697
00:52:06,710 --> 00:52:07,669
